{"tid":2241934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台改用中囯日語漢字","createTime":"2020-10-13T15:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T19:55:24.000Z","uid":36157,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0bee2eafc8c1b02e9012febdbef8a9dd91168eec","tid":2241934,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:53:00.000Z","msg":"最新風暴消息<br />\n(10月13日22:45 更新)<br />\n<br />\n浪卡繼續遠離香港。受東北季候風的影響，本港明日(十月十四日)初時會吹<strong><span class=\"x-large\">强</span></strong>風，離岸及高地亦間中吹烈風。預計三號<strong><span class=\"x-large\">强</span></strong>風信號會維持數小時。<br />\n<br />\n海面會有湧浪及非常大浪，市民應該遠離岸邊及停止所有水上活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://photouploads.com/images/EcLO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2FEcLO.png&h=298ef3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慢慢來，逐步增加唔會好覺。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cb6ca8fbbc96b81c5dbacf822cbcfbe53f4eff","tid":2241934,"uid":235277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:55:55.000Z","msg":"強"},{"pid":"0174f44ea816374411a234c3f787f79e70be61c7","tid":2241934,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efde822bed649c770d0db0cf3bb1c2499ec3741a","tid":2241934,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"慢慢成篇日語漢字都得<br />\n中囯人用偷改日語漢字係啱嘅"},{"pid":"c194b632bc1f971315d1a3b30539ea881377b8c0","tid":2241934,"uid":214679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:36:14.000Z","msg":"你講咩呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中囯日語漢字? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繁體中文字同日本漢字都將「强」字定為「強」字嘅異體字嘅寫法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QAOwkdc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQAOwkdc.png&h=113e3985&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4055a64e14b4981ff4479b660557fb1ff5b20ea8","tid":2241934,"uid":78429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c194b632bc1f971315d1a3b30539ea881377b8c0","tid":2241934,"uid":214679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:36:14.000Z","msg":"你講咩呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中囯日語漢字? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繁體中文字同日本漢字都將「强」字定為「強」字嘅異體字嘅寫法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QAOwkdc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQAOwkdc.png&h=113e3985&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"「强」喺日文好似係舊體，唔係異體"},{"pid":"db38521575fbb95005257f88bf33e6f8267d5f3a","tid":2241934,"uid":22609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:39:18.000Z","msg":"好核突個强字 唔知點解覺得好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過印象中字典見過"},{"pid":"94a40b4e07235274137eaebd466fef9a9fe1e150","tid":2241934,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:40:01.000Z","msg":"異體字姐"},{"pid":"d7637947141c9163c9b50b70366b756fb971c6c2","tid":2241934,"uid":249252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個fd個阿叔叫阿强<br />\n50幾歲土生土長香港人<br />\n身份證就係呢個强字<br />\n一出世就用而家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as